beauty&wellness.title: Bright-Eyed Pink Clay Under Eye Pads
beauty&wellness.productDetails: Crafted from natural pink clay, these reusable eye pads can be used hot or cold to soothe tired, puffy under-eyes and promote relaxation

beauty&wellness.title: Slip Silk Pillowcase
beauty&wellness.productDetails: Slip pure silk products are made using their proprietary blend of silk called slipsilk. This luxurious, hypoallergenic sham protects delicate facial skin and hair from the scratches, creases, and tugs caused by standard cotton, reducing split ends. Additionally, their proprietary blend of silk is designed to absorb less face cream, which keeps your skincare products, on your skin (where they belong)!

beauty&wellness.title: Mario Badescu Drying Lotion
beauty&wellness.productDetails: About Mario Badescu In 1967, Mario Badescu embarked on a mission to introduce European-style facials to upper echelon New York. His classic, Old World techniques - mastered in his native Romania - defined the essential relationship between skin health and beauty. In his revolutionary Upper East Side salon, Mario cared for each guest with customized treatments and personalized advice for at-home care. His understanding of the varying needs of differing complexions shaped the beloved line of masks, cleansers, lotions and serums that bear his name today. Each tried-and-true elixir is formulated with botanicals and fresh fruit extracts and addresses a full range of concerns, from acne to aging

beauty&wellness.title: Slip Mega Silk Scrunchies Set
beauty&wellness.productDetails: About Slip In 2003, Fiona Stewart was prescribed acne medication that resulted in extremely sensitive skin and thinning hair. Her dermatologist suggested that she sleep on a silk pillowcase. Unable to find one, Stewart sourced the best silk she could find and wrapped it around her pillow - the improvements to the health and radiance of both her hair and skin were so dramatic, she never looked back. The following year, Stewart and her partner Justin Dubois officially launched SLIP: the first silk pillowcase to be branded and marketed as a beauty product. Developed and refined for over ten years, the brand's signature slipsilk provides the ultimate combination of shine, thickness, softness, and durability for their line of pillowcases, sleep masks, and more.

beauty&wellness.title: Mario Badescu Facial Spray with Aloe, Chamomile, and Lavender
beauty&wellness.productDetails: Chamomile, vitamin C, and lavender blend for a nourishing elixir that brightens and soothes with a single spritz. It instantly revitalizes dry or lackluster skin and hair with a boost of moisture and dewy radiance. Use it for a makeup setting spray, to infuse an additional boost of dew into your moisturizer, or to refresh at your desk or on the go.  How to use: As needed, mist onto face and neck.

beauty&wellness.title: Tocca Mini Hand Cream
beauty&wellness.productDetails: Named after the Italian word for touch, fashion and fragrance house Tocca's exquisite scents evoke Old World romance and familiar places infused with the unexpected, fresh and new. Feminine through and through, their perfumes, scrubs and lotions are captured in charming vials and vessels that pretty up your dressing table along with your mystique.  Slather on this richly formulated hand cream anytime your skin requires some TLC. Packed with nourishing oils and shea butter, this concoction is ultra-hydrating and leaves behind a hint of one of Tocca's signature scents.

beauty&wellness.title: Deborah Lippmann True Colors Gel Lab Pro Nail Polish
beauty&wellness.productDetails: A healthier alternative to gel polish, this dual-patented formula combines the technology of Gel Lab Pro with ten active ingredients to help deliver long-lasting wear and shine without the use of lamps or extra tools.

beauty&wellness.title: Grown Alchemist SPF 30 Naturally Hydrating Sunscreen
beauty&wellness.productDetails: Formulated with mineral zinc oxide to provide broad spectrum protection, this reef-safe sunscreen a lightweight, ultra-sheer finish that blends effortlessly into your skin. Rich in vitamins, omega fatty acids, and antioxidants, it deeply nourishes and hydrates your skin to leave it feeling moisturized and soothed.

beauty&wellness.title: Anatomy of a Fragrance Eau De Parfum
beauty&wellness.productDetails: Well-blended and beautifully packaged, each decadent fragrance is designed to delight your senses with every spritz.  Gardenia Blanc: A floral blend of gardenia, orange flower, pink jasmine, and coconut milk. (FLORAL)  Honey Rose: A warm, romantic scent with notes of lily of the valley, sandalwood, and bergamot. (FLORAL)  Orchid Vanille: A bright, fresh combination of orange blossom, jasmine, black currant, and praline. (SPICE)  Tuberose Santal: A sensual blend of sandalwood and tuberose topped with notes of fig leaf. (SPICE)  Wild Fig: An exotic fusion of bergamot, pink pepper, lavender mint, and ginger. (SPICE)  Wildflower Bergamot: A zesty blend of bergamot, lemon, and mango layered with cedar and sandalwood. (FLORAL)

beauty&wellness.title: Mario Badescu Facial Spray with Aloe, Cucumber and Green Tea

beauty&wellness.title: Lavido Intimately Yours Wash
beauty&wellness.productDetails: Established in 2003 by herbalist Ido Magal, Lavido is an essential oil-based face and body company designed to promote positive change in the appearance of your skin. Using various technologies, including mechanical extraction and cold pressing, each elixir is formulated to retain only the best active ingredients from every botanical used. Better yet? This cruelty-free collection is dermatologically tested to ensure high quality and effectiveness.

beauty&wellness.title: PYT Beauty Bronzer Duo
beauty&wellness.productDetails: Wanting the best for their growing daughters' health and skin, best friends Mary Schulman and Amy Carr found themselves on a mission to create clean, pure cosmetics. To this end, they founded PYT Beauty, a collection of makeup and skincare products founded with the motto, "Beauty without the BS (bad stuff)." Subjected to an extensive process of research and testing, their final formulas feature only skin-safe ingredients, ensuring each elixir is one you can trust for not only your own skin, but for your loved ones, too.
